{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/xj5im8","slide":1,"text":"20 seconds\n\nThis project explores a reusable character customisation system for Unity. It currently exposes 38 body and facial morphs, supports male and female characters with independent recipes, and now accepts gameplay-driven muscle and body-fat values. The goal was not simply to make sliders work, but to organise the system so it can move beyond this one demo."}
