{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/e5n4bt","slide":6,"text":"85 seconds\n\nOpen the Body tab. First move Body Weight in both directions to show separate positive and negative blendshapes. Then move Muscle to show its zero-to-one behaviour. Adjust the female recipe, switch to male and make a different change, then switch back to prove recipe isolation. Change category tabs and show that the selection remains stable. Reset the active character and confirm the other recipe is unchanged. If time permits, invoke SetStatGrowth for muscle or body fat and show that it reaches the same controller path."}
